<div class="bg-cyan-800 pt-20 pb-2 lg:pb-4">
  <%= image_tag 'logo.png', class: 'mx-auto lg:w-3/5' %>
  <h1 class="text-gray-100 underline decoration-double text-right zen-kaku-medium tracking-wider mr-1 lg:mr-4 text-xl lg:text-4xl">
    日々の生活に、運動を
  </h1>
</div>

<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center mt-4">
  <div class="text-gray-800 text-center tracking-tight lg:tracking-wider lg:mr-8 mb-2 lg:mb-0">
    <h1 class="mb-1 lg:mb-4 zen-kaku-bold leading-8 text-xl lg:text-4xl">
      ウォーキング始めてみたはいいけど<br>今日はどこへいこう
    </h1>

    <%= link_to 'ログインせずに目的地を探してみる', new_gest_path, class: 'zen-kaku-regular lg:zen-kaku-medium underline decoration-orange-600 text-xl lg:text-2xl' %>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag 'man_in_distress.png', class: 'w-1/3 lg:w-1/12' %>
</div>

<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse justify-center items-center mt-12">
  <div class="text-gray-800 text-center tracking-wider lg:ml-8">
    <h1 class="text-center zen-kaku-regular leading-6 text-xl lg:text-4xl">
      Today's Courseなら<br>距離と種類を入力するだけで<br><span class="zen-kaku-bold">目的地が見つかる</span>
    </h1>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag 'man_using_smart_phone.png', class: 'w-1/3 lg:w-1/12' %>
</div>

<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center mt-12">
  <div class="text-gray-800 text-center tracking-wider lg:ml-8">
    <h1 class="text-center zen-kaku-regular leading-6 text-xl lg:text-4xl">
      ログインすれば<br>距離や時間を記録できるので<br><span class="zen-kaku-bold">モチベUPに繋がる</span>
    </h1>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag 'running_man.png', class: 'w-1/3 lg:w-1/12' %>
</div>

<div class="my-12 text-center flex flex-col lg:block">
  <%= link_to 'まずは試してみる', new_gest_path,
  class: 'orange-btn inline-block zen-kaku-medium tracking-widest text-xl py-3 lg:px-8 mx-10 lg:mx-0' %>

  <p class="inline-block zen-kaku-bold tracking-tighter text-2xl my-2 lg:my-0 mx-0 lg:mx-4">OR</p>

  <%= link_to '新規登録してみる', signup_path,
  class: 'orange-btn inline-block zen-kaku-medium tracking-widest text-xl py-3 lg:px-8 mx-10 lg:mx-0' %>
</div>

<div class="bg-cyan-800 py-6 lg:py-12 pl-4">
  <ul class="text-gray-100 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center">
    <li class="mb-4 lg:mb-0 lg:mr-12">利用規約(準備中)</li>
    <li class="mb-4 lg:mb-0 lg:mr-12">プライバシーポリシー(準備中)</li>
    <li>お問い合わせ(準備中)</li>
  </ul>
</div>
